lead_paragraph: Lionel Messi marked his retirement about face with a goal to give 10-man Argentina a 1-0 win over Uruguay on Thursday that lifted them to the top of the South American qualifying group for the 2018 World Cup finals in Russia.

headline.print_headline: Messi Goal Puts Argentina Top of World Cup Group
